sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Edge TLS
    participant Proxy as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant Validator as AllowlistValidator<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote vLLM Prefiller<br/>Dynamic port HTTP(S)
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: P/D Disaggregated Inference (NIXL v2 Protocol)

    Client->>Route: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (edge TLS terminated)

    alt SSRF Protection Enabled
        Proxy->>Validator: Validate prefill target
        Validator-->>Proxy: Allowed / Rejected (403)
    end

    Proxy->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Note right of Prefiller: Prefill phase:<br/>Compute KV cache
    Prefiller-->>Proxy: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>{remote_engine_id, block_ids,<br/>host, port}

    Proxy->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Body enriched with kv_transfer_params<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Note right of Decoder: Decode phase:<br/>Use transferred KV cache
    Decoder-->>Proxy: Inference result (streaming or batch)
    Proxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No x-prefiller-host-port header)

    Client->>Route: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no prefill header)
    Route->>Proxy: Forward
    Proxy->>Decoder: Passthrough to local decoder<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>Proxy: Inference result
    Proxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Validator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Maintenance (Background)

    loop Every 30s resync
        Validator->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool<br/>inference.networking.x-k8s.io/v1alpha2<br/>ServiceAccount token auth
        K8sAPI-->>Validator: InferencePool spec<br/>(label selectors)
        Validator->>K8sAPI: Watch Pods matching selectors
        K8sAPI-->>Validator: Pod IPs + names<br/>(add/update/delete events)
        Note right of Validator: Update in-memory<br/>IP/name allowlist
    end
